tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE Preprocessed_Data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    data_text TEXT,
    processed_data TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE Model_Parameters (
    model_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    parameter_name TEXT,
    parameter_value FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE Training_Logs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    training_time TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE Validation_Data (
    validation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    validation_result TEXT
)
